OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome early sunny spells, but
OL,6,Fcloud thickening and wind
OL,7,Fstrengthening ahead of a band of
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy rain sweeping east
OL,9,Facross the region. Sunny spells and
OL,10,Fisolated blustery showers in the
OL,11,Fafternoon, with a risk of hail and
OL,12,Fthunder.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA mostly cloudy and breezy
OL,15,Fnight, with outbreaks of rain and
OL,16,Fshowers continuing through the evening
OL,17,Fand early hours. Mild.
OL,18,
OL,19,CThursday:FA mixture of sunny spells
OL,20,Fand blustery showers, these perhaps
OL,21,Fheavy and thundery at times. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
