OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,6,Funsettled during this period.
OL,7,FOutbreaks of rain or showers will be
OL,8,Finterspersed with some drier and
OL,9,Fsunnier interludes. Occasionally
OL,10,Fwindy, especially Saturday.
OL,11,FTemperatures rather cool, trending
OL,12,Fnear normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
